       REM     ELSM09    BINARY INTEGER TO BCD CONVERTER    41 CARDS    ELSM0900
BINBCD SXD BINBCD+30,1              SAVE REGISTERS                      ELSM0901
       SXD BINBCD+31,2                                                  ELSM0902
       SXD BINBCD+32,4                                                  ELSM0903
       CAL 2,4                      BRING IN NUMBER OF WORDS TO CONVERT ELSM0904
       STP BINBCD+13                                                    ELSM0905
       PAX 0,1                      ENTER THIS NUMBER IN A REGISTER     ELSM0906
       ADD 1,4                      BRING IN ADDRESSES AND MODIFY       ELSM0907
       STA BINBCD+10                STORE MODIFIED ADDRESS              ELSM0908
       COM                                                              ELSM0909
       PDX 0,2                      STORAGE ADDRESS COMP TO B REGISTER  ELSM0910
