       LLS 0                        QUOTIENT SIGN TO ACCUMULATOR        ELSM0914
       CLM                          CLEAR ACCUMULATOR                   ELSM0915
       DVH BINBCD+39                FIND REMAINDER ON DIVISION BY TEN   ELSM0916
       ALS 36,4                     SHIFT REMAINDER TO PROPER POSITION  ELSM0917
       ADD 0,2                      ADD LOWER ORDER DIGITS              ELSM0918
       STO 0,2                      STORE LOW ORDER DIGITS              ELSM0919
       STQ COMMON                   TEST QUOTIENT TO SEE IF WORD HAS    ELSM0920
       CLA COMMON                   BEEN COMPLETELY CONVERTED, EMPTY    ELSM0921
